full_paths <- file.path(here(), dirs)
created <- logical(length(full_paths))

for (i in seq_along(full_paths)) {
  if (!dir.exists(full_paths[i])) {
    dir.create(full_paths[i], recursive = TRUE, showWarnings = FALSE)
    created[i] <- TRUE
  } else {
    created[i] <- FALSE
  }
}
